	quest.07238D6DC2A5D89D.quest_desc: [
		"Though safe from these creatures on the surface, deep under the water is another story. Giant &9Eels&r lurk in the depths of the &bIce Maze&r. They prey on those who sought to build shelter deep in the ice to escape the bitter wind. These creatures have been cursed to forever haunt these shelters and attack any who enter. The &9Eel&r remains in the water below the shelters, but will leap out to attack anyone and anything nearby."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&9Eels&r spawn underneath &8&kShelters&r in the &bIce Maze&r. You must go down into the bottom of the &8&kShelter&r."
	]
