	quest.1F72B0EC86701E8B.quest_desc: [
		"&6Super Glue&r bonds blocks together in moving contraptions."
		"Each use consumes durability. Connections remain until removed."
		""
		"&eChassis use&r"
		"Acts like a Slimeball for &6Linear&r or &6Radial Chassis&r."
		""
		"Right-click a chassis face to coat it with glue and attach blocks."
		"Sneak-right-click with an empty hand to remove the glue."
		""
		"&eArea mode&r"
		"Right-click one corner of an area, then the opposite corner to glue all blocks inside."
		""
		"Sneak-right-click to cancel the selection."
		""
		"While holding &6Super Glue&r, glued connections become visible."
		"Left-click them to remove the bond."
	]
