	quest.1F8257FBCD532E59.quest_desc: [
		"Wearing a full set of &eCardboard Armor&r transforms you into a simple box."
		"While disguised, mobs can’t see you unless you’re within &e1 block&r of them."
		""
		"&8●&r Perfect for hiding, sneaking, or confusing everything that wants you dead."
		""
		"&oSometimes the best armor is pretending you’re furniture.&o"
	]
