	quest.226608BC34917849.title: "Primordial Caves"
	quest.227E457B5462F06C.quest_desc: ["Train schedules allow for other mobs to control trains. Schedules can be configured by r-clicking while holding it. Any mob in a seat placed next to train controls can become a conducter. To turn a mob into a conducter, give it a configured train schedule. Blaze burners may become conducters from anywhere on the train."]
	quest.22AAE46659CE5A01.quest_desc: [
		"The &bSpellweaving Pickaxe&r is forged with Cthonic Gold and Earthen arcana."
		""
		"When primed, breaking a block spawns up to four loci."
		""
		"Loci seek and break nearby blocks of the same type."
		""
		"Ideal for clearing veins quickly."
	]
