	quest.23BB5B48E32B8A77.quest_desc: ["&eStarbuncle charm&r, crafted by &5Enchanting apparatus&r, can be right-clicked to summon a Starbuncle. The Starbuncle can be used to pick up and store items in chests using the &5Dominion wand&r. "]
	quest.23C0F5DDA0FF977A.quest_desc: [
		"As you arrive at the &5Tree&r, a surprisingly jovial voice rings out."
		""
		"&b\"Hero! Thank you for your efforts. I am the &5Tree of Wisdom&r&b, the one who sent the &2Voice of All Things&r&b to talk to you. You have done us a great service. &6Come to my hollow and have wisdom bestowed upon thou.\"&r"
	]
	quest.23C0F5DDA0FF977A.title: "A Whisper on the Winds IV"
	quest.242CA4FD15E0B853.quest_desc: ["{image:gamma_creatures:textures/screens/drazor_eng2.png width:150 height:100 align:center fit:true}"]
	quest.247F87052050822D.title: "Old Growth Bayou"
	quest.2483EC1E147FBD1E.quest_desc: [
		"At each of the sites of the &2Wildens&r, you find notes. It seems like someone has been researching them."
		""
		"Together, the notes say:"
		""
		"&b\"Place the &6Wilden Tablet&r&b onto the &6Ritual Pedestal&r\""
		"&b\"Grant it the fragments of each of the three types of Wilden\"&r"
		"&b\"And so shall the &5Great Beast&r&b be created\".&r&r"
		"&b\"Glory to the &7Invoker&r&b\".&r"
	]
	quest.2483EC1E147FBD1E.quest_subtitle: "You find notes..."
	quest.2483EC1E147FBD1E.title: "Chimeric Beast I"
	quest.24EFE0DCEE54E844.title: "Ice Spikes"
	quest.24F36F79FFF3F42E.quest_desc: [
		"The &6Water Wheel&r produces rotational power, generating Rotational Force when water flows across it."
		"As water moves steadily, the wheel spins, transferring power through shaft to connected machines."
		""
		""
		"The &6Large Water Wheel&r rotates at half the speed of a regular Water Wheel but doubles the stress capacity (&e512 SU&r vs. &e256 SU&r)."
		""
		"&8●&r Water Wheels can be stacked to increase power output, but more than 50 will break the setup."
		"&8●&r Tip: Combining smaller Water Wheels with a Large Water Wheel in the same network boosts both SU generation and rotational speed."
		""
		"&oHarness the flow wisely — too much water can drown even the strongest gears.&o"
	]
	quest.24F36F79FFF3F42E.quest_subtitle: "&oThe Flowing Engine&o"
	quest.24F36F79FFF3F42E.title: "Water Wheel"
	quest.24F53BF2381461F7.quest_desc: [
		"This is the final chapter for learning about automation! By now, you probably understand at least some of the fundamental concepts of &eCreate&r. To test your knowledge, your last challenge is to craft an advanced wireless terminal. It requires andesite, copper, brass, and sturdy sheets. No instructions this time, use what you've learned and the recipe tree in EMI to build this device. &2Good luck!&r"
		""
		"&l&bVoila!&r You have made a &l&eCreate Creation!&r"
		""
		"NOTE: You might want to add in a chunk loader near your inventory network so that you can actually access your storage from anywhere. "
	]
	quest.24F53BF2381461F7.quest_subtitle: "Advanced Wireless Terminal"
	quest.24F53BF2381461F7.title: "Practice Time"
	quest.251D21290027A466.quest_desc: [
		"The &6Crushing Wheels&r are an advanced alternative to the &6Millstone&r for crushing recipes."
		""
