	quest.252BFDFCE0877B3C.quest_desc: [
		"&dMending&r has now been restricted to &2Max Level Librarians&r only now. Because of this, there is a 1/3 chance that their final trade will be &dmending&r (or some variation of it). Villagers cycle their trades regularly, so it shouldn't take too long before at least one &2Max Level Librarian&r is selling it."
		""
		"&7There may be other ways to obtain this enchantment, however..."
	]
