	quest.27BE8047AD175D2A.quest_desc: [
		"- Place some vaults"
		"- Put &l&aitem hatch&r&r on it - You will need it to put items inside."
		"- Place &l&apackager&r&r on vault - to get items back."
		"- Place &l&astock ticker&r&r touching vault."
		"- Holding &l&2stock link&r&r - right click on stock ticker and place it on &lpackager&r."
		"- Place &l&aseat&r&r next to the stock ticker and put any mob (or blaze burner) on it. "
		""
