	quest.318C09F5262353EA.title: "Sky Arena"
	quest.31A496FE886348D5.title: "Pillager Camp"
	quest.31C2AAB08714196A.quest_desc: [
		"While exploring the world, you will encounter gateways leading to other dimensions."
		""
		"Materials found there are far more powerful and useful for reforging."
		""
		"To use them, you will need to upgrade your &6Reforging Table&r using an &5Obsidian Heart&r."
		""
		"These gateways are guarded by dangerous monsters, so &nprepare potions, strong food, golems, and any other tools you may need.&r"
	]
	quest.31C2AAB08714196A.quest_subtitle: "Dimensional challenges"
	quest.31C2AAB08714196A.title: "Gateways"
	quest.3231857C187C0EE1.quest_desc: ["The &3Ocean Monument&r holds the key to living beneath the waves, but the key remains guarded by &3three ancient sea creatures&r and their underlings. With bodies built for both defence and offense, the fight will not be an easy one for those unprepared for the water."]
	quest.3239F6FAEB0D15C2.quest_desc: [
		"With a reluctant gaze, you turn your back on the &6fleeing Illagers&r. "
		""
		"Perhaps this is for the best. You are likely not strong enough to take on the &5Illagers Fortress&r, and &ewill hopefully be rewarded&r for returning these &6Villagers&r back to safety. "
		""
		"You follow the &6Villagers&r as they point the way back to their home."
	]
	quest.3239F6FAEB0D15C2.quest_subtitle: "Incompatible with \"Seek Vengeance\""
	quest.3250EB72322E5124.quest_desc: [
		"This world is like the Overworld, but cursed by &5Liches&r to stay in eternal night. The moon changes the creatures, making them stronger and stranger."
		""
		"Portals were once made to spread corruption, but they were sealed. Now, only the &7guardians&r can open them. To pass, you must either defeat the guardian or pay their price."
	]
	quest.3250EB72322E5124.quest_subtitle: "The Land of Endless Night"
	quest.3250EB72322E5124.title: "&9&lStarlight Dimension&r"
	quest.326769D46FEDCE7B.quest_desc: [
		"You can craft one of this one easily, allows You for teleportation to Your grave."
		"You can upgrade &dKnowledge of Death&r skill so there's a change to have one right after dying."
	]
	quest.326769D46FEDCE7B.quest_subtitle: "One one the most useful items"
	quest.327C2F098771B7C3.title: "Deep Dark"
	quest.32A412608013191D.quest_subtitle: "Nightfallen Dominion ability. Eldritch and Blood school bonuses"
	quest.32A412608013191D.title: "Forlorn Harbinger Armor"
	quest.32BC483761E19582.quest_desc: ["This book is your guide to Iron's Spells and Spellbooks. Although some things have been modified or outright removed, using this in tandem with JEI/EMI and the &e\"Wizardry\"&r quests should give you a good understanding of how &dBattle Magic&r works."]
	quest.32BC483761E19582.title: "Iron's Guidebook"
	quest.32EBDF1D9140CFB0.quest_subtitle: "&l&n&5The final backpack"
