		"Prevents hunger loss, except when using saturation to regenerate health."
		"Eathing food with nourishment can lead to &5permanent&r health gain (one time effect per food)."
	]
	quest.3720BAEAD39CB12E.title: "Nourishment"
	quest.3742FE67B8DE9261.quest_desc: ["Upgraded armor turn this set into high utilities armor with cool appearance, &5Runic Spanner&r can be use to config placed rune"]
	quest.3742FE67B8DE9261.title: "Technicaly mage?"
	quest.375CFCF95E57AC3D.title: "Monolith"
	quest.379A48ACDCA454C9.quest_desc: [
		"&bSoulstained Steel&r is created by attuning iron with &bSoulstone&r."
		""
		"Items made from this metal can strike the soul directly."
		""
		"It is used to craft advanced weapons and armor."
		""
		"Raw contact is unstable, so it must be properly forged before use."
	]
	quest.379A48ACDCA454C9.quest_subtitle: "Metal infused with Soulstone"
	quest.379A48ACDCA454C9.title: "Soulstained Steel"
	quest.379A85A584B88A2E.quest_desc: ["Feed any bee 48 times with a sugar-like item or a honey bottle."]
