	]
	quest.7A413E106A44B9B8.quest_subtitle: "Flame-driven speed"
	quest.7A61DCA5D60B5A6E.quest_desc: [
		"Hidden deep within the oceans lies the mysterious Origin Island, a forgotten land tied to the origins of familiars."
		""
		"Only tiny wandering souls live there—unfinished forms of familiars that never reached their final evolution."
		""
		"These fragile spirits can be captured using Empty Bottles and are required for powerful rituals."
		""
		""
		""
		"To discover the island, you will first need a &bSniffer&r."
		"Occasionally, a Sniffer may dig up rare &bCrystal Berries&r."
		""
		"Feeding these berries to a tamed familiar awakens memories of its origin, forming &bMemory Fragments&r."
		""
		"These fragments behave similarly to Eyes of Ender, guiding you toward the hidden &bOrigin Island&r."
	]
	quest.7A61DCA5D60B5A6E.quest_subtitle: "First: Find Sniffer"
	quest.7A61DCA5D60B5A6E.title: "Onto Origin Island"
	quest.7AFD5307EE32AAF1.title: "Dark Coven"
	quest.7B33A0B7B0475946.quest_desc: ["A pink lotus found beside lilypads, carrying a soft aura and soothing scent. Once used in ritual fires as offerings, or to ward off monsters, sickness, and corruption."]
	quest.7B33A0B7B0475946.quest_subtitle: "Lotus of Calm"
	quest.7B3D68BB8425ABC4.title: "Baba Yaga Hut"
	quest.7B6D24D7F57E065A.quest_desc: [
		"As your resources grow, traditional storage becomes insufficient."
		""
		"Alien technology from the &9Starlight Dimension&r combined with electricity allows you to store immense amounts of items, automate production, and access your storage instantly from anywhere across dimensions."
		""
		"Unlocks &6Advanced Storage&r chapter."
	]
	quest.7B6D24D7F57E065A.quest_subtitle: "Advanced storage systems"
	quest.7B6D24D7F57E065A.title: "Digital Storage"
	quest.7B8A69CF40851993.title: "Oasis Village"
	quest.7B93DF7B1EE96E10.quest_desc: ["Cheap cost and fun, this build can get you safe, easy and low cost at once but will not work well with teammate since these undead creature are aggressive most of the time so you are most likely solo play with this build."]
	quest.7B93DF7B1EE96E10.quest_subtitle: "You may want to get a Novice spell book and a flimsy journal atleast before go for this build"
	quest.7C34DFBE6F2EE123.quest_desc: ["Complete red &4Sempiternal Sanctum&r challenge."]
	quest.7C5A652995E2A1FA.title: "Umvuthana Grove"
	quest.7CD7CC37603B916F.quest_subtitle: "&l&n&5A step to &eimmortality?&r"
	quest.7CFFD768262D0F38.quest_subtitle: "Allows for hovering and gliding"
	quest.7D4E62ABAD4362C1.quest_desc: ["A wireless terminal allowd you to access your inventory as long as you are within 16 blocks of it. No longer will you have to bounce back between your enchanting setup, kitchen, and storage. Now you can access it at the push of a button!"]
	quest.7D50FAAF3BE2F729.quest_desc: ["{image:gamma_creatures:textures/screens/dosmo_eng2.png width:150 height:100 align:center fit:true}"]
	quest.7D83D800633DF5BA.quest_subtitle: "Kill 100 Zombie"
	quest.7D83D800633DF5BA.title: "Undead Slayer"
	quest.7DBC8A2160706F39.quest_desc: ["Start worshipping, may be somewhere out there will respond back to you. First wear uniform"]
	quest.7DBC8A2160706F39.title: "Worship"
	quest.7E1893A68247C7F2.quest_desc: [
		"The &6Mechanical Pump&r pushes fluids through &6Fluid Pipes&r."
		""
		"Each pump can move fluids up to 16 blocks."
		"Place another pump to continue the line."
		""
		"The brown arrows show the flow direction."
		"Use a &6Wrench&r to reverse it."
		""
		""
		"&eFluid Pipes&r"
		"Used to transport fluids between tanks and machines."
		""
		"Pipes can carry only one fluid type at a time."
		""
		"Pipes placed next to each other connect automatically."
		"To prevent connections you can:"
		""
		"• make the pipe transparent with a &6Wrench&r"
		"• apply &6Copper Casing&r"
		"• attach &6Brackets&r"
		""
		"Copper Casing can also lock pipe corners, preventing automatic connections."
	]
	quest.7E1893A68247C7F2.quest_subtitle: "Fluid movement"
	quest.7E67CBAC42F3DD58.quest_desc: [
		"Starlight is a dimension unlike any other."
		""
		"Within it you may discover lost golem technology, allowing you to digitize your storage."
		""
		"Its materials are infused with far stronger magic than those found in the Overworld."
		""
		"Unlocks &6Eternal Starlight&r chapter"
	]
	quest.7E67CBAC42F3DD58.quest_subtitle: "Sky full of stars"
	quest.7E67CBAC42F3DD58.title: "The Starlight Dimension"
	quest.7E7A6356E4B330CD.quest_desc: [
		"The &6Encased Chain Drive&r transfers rotational power, similar to a Mechanical Belt but with more flexible layouts."
		""
		"Multiple drives can be placed in a straight horizontal or vertical line to form a chain."
		"Rotation passes through all connected blocks."
		""
		"Use a &6Wrench&r to switch between horizontal and vertical orientation."
		""
		"Encased Chain Drives can also connect to &6Adjustable Chain Gearshifts&r, allowing rotation speed to be controlled with redstone."
	]
	quest.7E7A6356E4B330CD.quest_subtitle: "Flexible power transmission"
	quest.7EA6DF4DD6B53096.quest_subtitle: "Grudge ability. Eldritch and Ice school bonuses"
	quest.7EA6DF4DD6B53096.title: "Cursed Wraithguard Armor"
	quest.7EEB451F21DD14AE.quest_desc: [
		"Deployers can act as a player when it comes the world interactions. They can use weapons like swords, and tools like shears. R-click with a wrench to toggle between acting as a l-click (attack/destroy) and r-click (place). R-click with the weapon/tool/item on the brass hand's hitbox to give it to the depoyer."
		""
		"Deployers are also a very important tool for recipe sequences. Many recipe  sequences require items to be deployed on whatever is processing. This works for items on belts and depots. Chutes placed above deployers can provide them with more items if needed."
	]
	quest.7EF9437C1043052C.quest_desc: [
		"A sacred knife that deals extra damage to ender creatures and increases the chance of rare drops."
		""
		"By holding right-click, it may also reveal hidden plants among the ordinary."
	]
	quest.7EF9437C1043052C.quest_subtitle: "Ritual Blade"
	quest.7F0321F6C37A19B7.quest_desc: [
		"This pack comes with a lot of keybinds built in. &lHere are some of key ones:"
		""
		"- &d\"B\"&r - Open Backpack (&eSoph. Backpacks&r)"
		"- &d\"C\"&r - Open Spellbook (&eArs Nouveau&r)"
		"- &d\"N\"&r - Cast Selected Spell (&eIron's S 'n S&r)"
		"- &d\"R\"&r - Roll/Dodge (&eCombat Roll&r)"
		"- &d\"Button 4\"&r - Cycles Offhand Slot (&eInventorio&r)"
		"- &d\"M\"&r - Open World Map (&eXaero's World Map&r)"
		"- &d\"Y\"&r - Minimap Settings (&eXaero's Minimap&r)"
		"- &d\"I\"&r - Inventory Settings Menu (&eInventorio&r)."
		"- &d\"K\"&r - Rotation Lock (&eQuark&r)"
		""
		"&a&lCommon Default Conflicting Keybinds:&r&r"
		"- &6\"R\"&r - Roll/Dodge (&eCombat Roll&r)"
		"- &6\"R\"&r - Open Spell Wheel (&eIron's S 'n S&r)"
		"- &3\"B\"&r - Open Backpack (&eSoph. Backpacks&r)"
		"- &3\"B\"&r - Open Storage Terminal (&eTom's SS&r)"
		"- &3\"B\"&r - New Waypoint (&eXaero's Minimap&r)"
		""
		"&bContinue on Next Page -->"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&a&lYou might want to add a keybind to:&r&r"
		"- Switch hotbars (&eQuark&r). Search it at \"Hotbar Swapper\" under Keybinds."
		"- Switch utilities (&eInventorio&r). This scrolls through your offhand slot. Search it at \"Utility\" under Keybinds."
		""
		"If you have any questions on how to control something, check the Key Binds!"
		""
		"Some items with specific keybinds (ie. &bQuiver&r, &bMap Atlas&r) have additional information on them in their JEI Information tab."
	]
	quest.7F0321F6C37A19B7.quest_subtitle: "All current keybinds of note!"
	quest.7F0321F6C37A19B7.title: "Keybinds"
	quest.7F0B971E7ABC0DEE.quest_desc: [
		"The &6Mechanical Pipette&r works like a &6Mechanical Arm&r but transfers fluids instead of items."
		""
		"It can move fluids between nearby fluid containers."
		""
		"Some fluid storages cannot be accessed directly."
		"In those cases, use &6Fluid Interfaces&r."
	]
	quest.7F0B971E7ABC0DEE.quest_subtitle: "Fluid handling"
	quest.7F71C0CB020ACA4D.quest_desc: ["Shares chests/vaults (etc.) inventories to network. Place blaze burner/seat with mob on it and You can order those things! You'll need packager to extract stuff from inside."]
	quest.7F972B3D9AF131FC.quest_desc: [
		"The Nether is necessary to obtain materials such as quartz."
		""
		"Structures found there may contain useful tools and resources."
		""
		"Beware though — hellfire has forged some of the strongest monsters you will face."
		""
		"Unlocks &6The Nether&r chapter"
	]
	quest.7F972B3D9AF131FC.quest_subtitle: "Hostile realm"
	quest.7F972B3D9AF131FC.title: "Dimension Basics"
	quest.7FD332F870142F0F.quest_desc: [
		"&bRune Of Unnatural Stamina&r increases movement speed."
		""
		"Allows sprinting even at low hunger."
	]
